title: Daily Routines and Serial Killers

description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

In this episode, Kate and Leisha ask each other hard hitting questions! From unraveling Kate’s mysterious night routine to stumbling upon the not-so-fun fact that Leisha’s childhood involved a serial killer that ruined her paper route…amongst other things.
